query:
INSERT INTO tokens (index, token_index_per_contract, token_address, contract_index, contract_sub_index, total_supply, token_id, init_transaction_index)
                    VALUES (
                        (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(index) + 1, 0) FROM tokens),
                        (SELECT COALESCE(MAX(token_index_per_contract) + 1, 0) FROM tokens WHERE contract_index = $2 AND contract_sub_index = $3),
                        $1, 
                        $2, 
                        $3, 
                        $4, 
                        $5, 
                        $6
                    )
                    ON CONFLICT (token_address)
                    DO UPDATE SET total_supply = tokens.total_supply + EXCLUDED.total_supply
